EventBridge, create a rule with the following event pattern:
json
Copy code
{
 "detail": {
 "eventName": ["ConsoleLogin"],
 "userIdentity": {
 "type": ["Root"]
 },
 "responseElements": {
 "ConsoleLogin": ["Success"]
 }
 }
}
This ensures that only root user login events trigger the rule
